   {[}111-B2-041]; Agencia Espafiola de Cooperacion Internacional y de
   Desarrollo (AECI) {[}D/027406/09, D/033858]},
Funding-Text = {The Guides and Scouts Association of Costa Rica granted permission to
   conduct the research at the Iztaru Camp at Cerros La Carpintera. Gilbert
   Barrantes and Diego Ocampo (UCR) identified the hummingbirds. Two
